        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 3. Centrodorsal and radials in Himerometridae A.H. Clark, 1908. A–D. Himerometra robustipinna (Carpenter, 1881) (MNHN-IE-2012-862). A. Adoral side of centrodorsal. B. Cirrus sockets on lateral face of centrodorsal.C–D. Radials.C. Adoral view showing vermiculate grooves on inner face.D. Distal articular facet. E. Discometra rhodanica (Fontannes, 1877) from Picabrier (MHNL 20.062687), cirrus sockets on centrodorsal. Scale bars: A–D = 1 mm; E = 0.5 mm." ;
